{"tid":2000933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"15歲國中生體育課上突猝死！　爸媽腿軟：「戴口罩」跑步是致死因","createTime":"2020-05-04T07:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T03:32:30.000Z","uid":166360,"like":176,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"0014edf17f492615374e6a2453943c639835cb8f","tid":2000933,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:36:32.000Z","msg":"記者鄭思楠／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n疫情趨緩，大陸多個省份相繼迎來返校復課，但是在校期間，學生們的口罩防護是否可以鬆懈又成為了新的爭議性話題。日前，2位國中生在體育課上因為戴著口罩跑步而猝死。社交網路上，已經有大量文章批評上體育課仍要求學生戴口罩的做法錯誤，指責這是形式主義。<br />\n<br />\n據《華商報》報導，4月24日，河南鄲城縣一名15歲學生在體育課上猝死。4月30日，學生家長查看監視器畫面發現孩子事發時戴著口罩跑步，懷疑這就是死因。校方表示，希望進行屍檢但未被同意，經過協商，最終賠償37萬人民幣（約新台幣157萬元）達成和解。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200504/1705871.htm?from=mweb-newsshare-fb&amp;fbclid=IwAR29Ca_ajgb0xaOST2X7GABy7YLoeLOtsHYMoq5vj3VGVexr9ZeKno4ef9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200504%2F1705871.htm%3Ffrom%3Dmweb-newsshare-fb%26fbclid%3DIwAR29Ca_ajgb0xaOST2X7GABy7YLoeLOtsHYMoq5vj3VGVexr9ZeKno4ef9I&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=0d940ed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200504/1705871.htm?from=mweb-newsshare-fb&amp;fbclid=IwAR29Ca_ajgb0xaOST2X7GABy7YLoeLOtsHYMoq5vj3VGVexr9ZeKno4ef9I</a>"},{"pid":"1d0fd2c23c6963bb46e6c50ab2205c0a496dede3","tid":2000933,"uid":119596,"like":472,"dislike":4,"score":468,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:38:58.000Z","msg":"都解封啦, 仲戴咩口罩啫, 仲要戴N95, 仲要劇烈運動, 大佬呀, 你想點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b724b9aa4d0bf8fd0bf96011d43b1fa9e0e47b61","tid":2000933,"uid":105678,"like":7,"dislike":80,"score":-73,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:41:14.000Z","msg":"連登仲有班人話戴口罩做尖，一睇就知係衫架發言"},{"pid":"b61aab7655953489ff1ec0223710a5df63027f72","tid":2000933,"uid":30379,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"quote":{"pid":"1d0fd2c23c6963bb46e6c50ab2205c0a496dede3","tid":2000933,"uid":119596,"like":472,"dislike